					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“Can’t do anything about getting thrown in the slammer. Let’s eat our pork cutlet rice bowls and figure out how to bust out of here.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“都被关进来了，也没办法⋯⋯总之就先吃猪排饭后，再来打算吧。”",
